column1: University of Kentucky Football Game Traffic Conditions

column4: Roadway shutdown between Sports Center Dr and Kastle Rd due to a serious injury collision.
Three lanes outbound and one lane inbound from 3 p.m. to 5 p.m. for post-game traffic.
Outbound left turn to Alumni Dr is closed.

column3: Tates Creek Rd at Alumni Dr:
column4: Traffic from the stadium MUST turn right on Tates Creek Rd.
